Italian Alex Bellini will live atop an iceberg off the coast of North West Greenland starting next year . 
 He will stay in isolation inside a contained ball without opening the hatch for 12 months . 
 The capsule will contain supplies and equipment for his survival, and workout equipment to keep him fit . 
 Its designed to survive harsh conditions - such as the iceberg flipping - and can also float in water . 
 